    <ThingDef Name="MP_3008_GA" ParentName="BaseMakeableGun_GA">
        <defName>Gun_MP_3008_GA</defName>
        <label>MP 3008</label>
        <description>Also known as the Volksmaschinenpistole, the weapon was closely based on the Sten Mk II submachine gun, except for its vertical magazine; some had additional pistol grips. The MP 3008 was an emergency measure, designed at a time when Germany was at the point of collapse. Desperately short of raw materials, the Germans sought to produce a radically cheaper alternative to their standard submachine gun, the MP 40.</description>
